[30;1m572 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m573 | [0m[35m        will sort by ``category``, ``title`` (in descending order) and[0m
[30;1m574 | [0m[35m        ``price`` in ascending order using the ``avg`` mode.[0m
[30;1m575 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m576 | [0m[35m        The API returns a copy of the Search object and can thus be chained.[0m

[30;1m117 | [0m[35m    the timeout is over the connection will be resurrected and returned to the[0m
[30;1m118 | [0m[35m    live pool. A connection that has been previously marked as dead and[0m
[30;1m119 | [0m[35m    succeeds will be marked as live (its fail count will be deleted).[0m
